		<p>AI, I agree with you that certain tasks are best done in one sitting.  A compromise between bursts and long stretches could be daily, 2-3 hour stretches.  While a typical knowledge worker won&#8217;t get a whole day to work on a project, it may be feasible to train your colleagues to know that you&#8217;ll be unreachable between 2 and 5.</p>

